Association analysis was carried out using various regression and mixed models in GenStat (GENSTAT 2005). First, the adjusted means of each trait were extracted in a model that corrects the observations for the conditions of a specific trial (company performing the trial and year of the trial):\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
